Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.72,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Cactus 1549.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.60,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}跑道4，可以起飞{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Runway four. Cleared for takeoff.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.52,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549，可以起飞{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Cactus 1549. Cleared for takeoff.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.28,中文,,0,0,0,,“SOS”，全美航空1549\N{\r英文}Mayday, mayday. Cactus 1549.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:32.96,中文,,0,0,0,,双发停车，是双发\N{\r英文}We've lost both engines. Both engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:38.97,中文,,0,0,0,,1发和2发重新启动失败\N{\r英文}No relight on one or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.32,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549，如果我们能给你清空跑道{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Cactus 1549, if we can get it for you,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.13,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你能尝试降落在跑道13吗？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}do you wanna try to land runway 1-3?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.32,中文,,0,0,0,,离场管制，我们没法办到\N{\r英文}Departure control, we can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们现在返回拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}We're turning back towards LaGuardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:05.00,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉瓜迪亚塔台，全美航空1549，尝试降落跑道13{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}LaGuardia Tower, Cactus 1549, trying to make 1-3.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.68,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}萨利，我们太低了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Sully, we're too low.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:08.36,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利，我们太低了\N{\r英文}Sully, we're too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:09.72,中文,,0,0,0,,稳住\N{\r英文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:24.60,中文,,0,0,0,,加把劲\N{\r英文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:31.92,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利\N{\r英文}Sully!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.36,中文,,0,0,0,,洛丽，我爱你\N{\r英文}Lorrie, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.07,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}萨利机长{\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.07,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8}翻译：danassus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你有什么毛病啊？\N{\r英文}What the hell's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:20.01,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}机上载有乘客150人{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}The onboard count, 150 passengers,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}加上3名空乘人员和2位驾驶员{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}three flight attendants and two pilots, one of whom,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.41,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}其中高级驾驶员凭借自己的经验和技术{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}the senior pilot, drew on all of his experience and skill,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}再加上奇迹般的好运{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}which combined with near-miraculous good luck{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}结局简直是让人惊叹不已{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}and a result that was, frankly, astounding.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}部分受伤乘客并无生命危险{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}There were some non-critical injuries,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.09,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可每个人，每个人都幸免于难{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}but everyone, everyone, survived.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549号航班的首张画面...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}The first pictures of US Airways Flight 1549 reveal...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你以为自己要死了，绝望了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}You think that you're gonna die. That's what you think.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:43.57,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可奇迹般的又捡回条命{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}And then, miraculously, you don't.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.60,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}谢谢你，机长{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Thank you, Captain.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}谢谢你，谢谢{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Thank{\i} you, {\i1}thank{\i} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.64,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，谢谢大家的到来，谢谢\N{\r英文}Okay, thank you, everybody, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.88,中文,,0,0,0,,感谢机长萨伦伯格今天能来\N{\r英文}Thank you, Captain Sullenberger, for being here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我们也要欢迎副驾驶斯基尔斯\N{\r英文}We also wanna welcome First Officer Skiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.68,中文,,0,0,0,,很高兴你今天能赶来\N{\r英文}I'm glad you could make it in this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我们才是最开心能来的吧？\N{\r英文}Not as glad as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}首先说明，我们有飞机系统小组{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}For the record, we had an Aircraft Systems Team{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.04,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}参与这起调查{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}on this investigation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.88,中文,,0,0,0,,还有飞机结构组，维护检修组\N{\r英文}Also Aircraft Structures, MRT,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.92,中文,,0,0,0,,飞机性能组，空中交通管制\N{\r英文}Aircraft Performance, ATC,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.05,中文,,0,0,0,,野生动物因素，存活因素，应急响应\N{\r英文}Wildlife Factors, Survival Factors and Emergency Response.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.84,中文,,0,0,0,,今天我们先着手进行人员表现的调查\N{\r英文}Today, we begin with our operation and human performance investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,涉及全美航空1549号航班的坠机事故\N{\r英文}on the crash of US Airways Flight 1549.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.68,中文,,0,0,0,,- 水上迫降   - 机长？\N{\r英文}- Water landing.  - Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.68,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是坠机，是水面迫降\N{\r英文}This was not a crash and it wasn't a ditching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们清楚自己在做什么\N{\r英文}We knew what we were trying to execute here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是...\N{\r英文}It was not a...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.44,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是坠机，是水面迫降\N{\r英文}It was not a crash. It was a forced water landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么不尝试返回拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}Why didn't you attempt to return to LaGuardia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.40,中文,,0,0,0,,显然没有足够的高度\N{\r英文}There simply was not enough altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:48.21,中文,,0,0,0,,只有哈德逊河足够长，足够平\N{\r英文}The Hudson was the only place that was long enough and smooth enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.72,中文,,0,0,0,,和足够宽，来冒险尝试把飞机安全降落\N{\r英文}and wide enough to even attempt to land the airplane safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:51.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}空管证实{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Air Traffic testified{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你曾说要返回拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}that you stated you were returning to LaGuardia,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.56,中文,,0,0,0,,可并未执行\N{\r英文}but you did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.40,中文,,0,0,0,,在我开始左转后\N{\r英文}As I began the left turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:02.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我意识到是飞不回去的\N{\r英文}I realized I couldn't make it back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.00,中文,,0,0,0,,并且也会断了各种后路\N{\r英文}and it would have eliminated all the other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.04,中文,,0,0,0,,返回拉瓜迪亚绝对是个错误\N{\r英文}Returning to LaGuardia would have been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.60,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，给我们讲讲你是怎么计算那些参数的\N{\r英文}Okay, well, let's get into how you calculated all those parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:09.92,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}根本没有时间去计算{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}There was no time for calculating.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我不得不依赖自己这四十多年来，从上千次飞行中积累下来的\N{\r英文}I had to rely on my experience of managing the altitude and speed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.88,中文,,0,0,0,,对高度和速度的掌控经验\N{\r英文}of thousands of flights over four decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这么说你没有做任何的...\N{\r英文}You're saying you didn't do any...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我目测了一下\N{\r英文}I eyeballed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你目测？\N{\r英文}You eyeballed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.48,中文,,0,0,0,,对\N{\r英文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.61,中文,,0,0,0,,那条河是机上乘客生还的最大希望\N{\r英文}The best chance those passengers had was on that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我决定豪赌一把\N{\r英文}And I'd bet my life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.08,中文,,0,0,0,,事实就是这样\N{\r英文}In fact, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我还会再赌一次\N{\r英文}And I would do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.96,中文,,0,0,0,,根据航空工程师的推算\N{\r英文}Aviation engineers are theorizing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你有足够的动力抵达跑道\N{\r英文}you had enough energy to make it back to a runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.80,中文,,0,0,0,,工程师不等于飞行员\N{\r英文}Well, engineers are not pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.61,中文,,0,0,0,,他们搞错了\N{\r英文}They're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.53,中文,,0,0,0,,而且他们也不在现场\N{\r英文}And they weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,先不管了，考虑各种可能性\N{\r英文}Regardless, we have to follow up on all implications
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.76,中文,,0,0,0,,是我们调查的需要\N{\r英文}as part of our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的计算机会应用返航场景算法\N{\r英文}Our computers will run return scenario algorithms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.17,中文,,0,0,0,,这样就能用和你们相同的参数生成模拟\N{\r英文}It'll generate simulations with your exact parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.20,中文,,0,0,0,,双发停转，高度\N{\r英文}The dual engine loss, the altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你做出抉择时所面对的一切\N{\r英文}Everything you faced when you made your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我想旁观这些计算机模拟\N{\r英文}I would like to oversee those computer simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.68,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}调查期间可安排不了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Not possible during an investigation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你说因遭飞鸟多次撞击\N{\r英文}You stated that it was a dual engine failure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.04,中文,,0,0,0,,造成双发停车？\N{\r英文}due to multiple bird strikes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这是前所未有的情况\N{\r英文}That would be unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:13.48,中文,,0,0,0,,凡事皆有头一回嘛\N{\r英文}Well, everything is unprecedented until it happens for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你头天晚上睡了几个小时?\N{\r英文}How much sleep did you get the night before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.05,中文,,0,0,0,,8小时的好觉\N{\r英文}Eight hours. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你的血糖有可能偏低吗？\N{\r英文}Is it possible your blood sugar was low?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我精神饱满，思维敏锐，对周围环境了如指掌\N{\r英文}I was rested, alert and completely aware of my surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.13,中文,,0,0,0,,你上一次饮酒是什么时候？机长萨伦伯格\N{\r英文}When was your last drink, Captain Sullenberger?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.32,中文,,0,0,0,,9天前\N{\r英文}Nine days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.48,中文,,0,0,0,,有滥用药物吗？\N{\r英文}Drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:30.68,中文,,0,0,0,,没，从没有过\N{\r英文}No. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.17,中文,,0,0,0,,副驾驶斯基尔斯？\N{\r英文}First Officer Skiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.32,中文,,0,0,0,,不喝酒，一直如此\N{\r英文}Uh, don't drink. Never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,机长，你家里最近有什么烦心事吗？\N{\r英文}Captain, have you had any troubles at home lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.80,中文,,0,0,0,,家家都有本难念的经\N{\r英文}No more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,这从不会影响到我工作\N{\r英文}And nothing that affected my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.76,中文,,0,0,0,,真是荒唐\N{\r英文}It's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:57.40,中文,,0,0,0,,他们为什么想找我们的过错？结果不是皆大欢喜吗\N{\r英文}Why are they looking for something we did wrong when it all turned out right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.68,中文,,0,0,0,,航空公司和他们的保险公司\N{\r英文}It didn't turn out all right for the airline
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.12,中文,,0,0,0,,可欢喜不起来\N{\r英文}and their insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.00,中文,,0,0,0,,对此我们要有心理准备\N{\r英文}We should expect some blowback.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:05.05,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吧，麦克，他们还能怎么说？他不该去挽救大家？\N{\r英文}Come on, Mike. What are they gonna say? That he shouldn't have saved everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.85,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是针对我们，国家运输安全委员会只是照章办事\N{\r英文}It's not personal. NTSB's just doing its job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:10.89,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦他们收集到完整的证据，自会消停的\N{\r英文}Once they have all the facts, it'll calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.20,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利\N{\r英文}Sully,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.48,中文,,0,0,0,,他们应该给你颁奖，送你回去工作\N{\r英文}they should pin on the medal and send you back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.05,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉，邮箱已经满了\N{\r英文}Sorry. This mailbox is full.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.36,中文,,0,0,0,,今早到现在，我没再给罗琳打电话，好像其他人都打了\N{\r英文}I didn't call Lorrie since this morning. Apparently everyone else did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.92,中文,,0,0,0,,不是有意打扰你们，不过我很想说一句\N{\r英文}Not meaning to bother, but I have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.04,中文,,0,0,0,,能给你开车真是荣幸\N{\r英文}it is an honor driving you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.80,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.68,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}今年都是些什么破事啊？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}What has it been this year so far?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.48,中文,,0,0,0,,伯纳德·麦道夫，两场战争仍未结束，几百万人找不到工作\N{\r英文}Bernie Madoff, two wars without end. Many million new people with no work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:33.48,中文,,0,0,0,,设计一种庞兹骗局，令投资者损失500亿美元以上，其中包括众多大型金融机构
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这还只是1月份的头2周\N{\r英文}And that's just the first two weeks of January.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.88,中文,,0,0,0,,可看看这周五的头条？太鼓舞人心了\N{\r英文}Friday's headline? This is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.41,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，麦克，我们让这个司机去做人品证人怎么样\N{\r英文}Hey, Mike. How about we add the driver as a character witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.48,中文,,0,0,0,,终于打来了\N{\r英文}Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.24,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r英文}Yeah, finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.68,中文,,0,0,0,,国家运输安全委员会耗了我们一天\N{\r英文}The NTSB had us tied up all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.44,中文,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\r英文}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我只想听下你的声音\N{\r英文}I just needed to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.44,中文,,0,0,0,,听别人的都听烦了\N{\r英文}I've been hearing everybody else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你现在有好多侄子啊，想不到吧{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}You'd be amazed how many cousins you have.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不像是我们家的啊\N{\r英文}It doesn't feel much like family here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我这里还算平静\N{\r英文}Pretty quiet here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:25.76,中文,,0,0,0,,记者想让我分享下你现在的心境\N{\r英文}The reporters want me to give an update inside the mind of Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我该跟他们说点什么？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}What should I tell them?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.05,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}洛丽，告诉他们你无权透露什么{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Lorrie, tell them you're not allowed to talk to anybody.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.80,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我听不清你说什么  - 洛丽，我...\N{\r英文}- Look, I can't hear you.  - Lorrie, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- 我听不清你说什么{\i}  - 我想跟你说\N{\r英文}{\i1}- I can't hear you. Call me back.{\i}  - I'm trying to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.08,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你不需要开口{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}you do not have to talk to anybody.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我听不清，过会儿再打给我\N{\r英文}I can't hear you. Call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.80,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}洛丽，我想说...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Lorrie, I'm trying to tell...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嘿,机长萨利！{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Hey, Captain Sully!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.37,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- 机长萨利！  - 萨利！{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}- Captain Sully!  - Sully!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:51.89,中文,,0,0,0,,作为奇迹的创造者，你现在是什么感受？\N{\r英文}How does it feel to be a miracle maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.32,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利，就问一个问题！\N{\r英文}Sully, one question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.52,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你是怎么完成这个壮举的？  - 萨利！\N{\r英文}- How did you pull off the impossible?  - Sully!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.92,中文,,0,0,0,,机长萨利！萨利！\N{\r英文}Captain Sully! Sully!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:00.20,中文,,0,0,0,,请让下\N{\r英文}Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.60,中文,,0,0,0,,机长萨利！\N{\r英文}{\i1}Captain Sully!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.16,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我打算开车撞走这些媒体{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I'm thinking about running over the press with the car.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.52,中文,,0,0,0,,算正当防卫，你觉得陪审团会定我的罪吗？\N{\r英文}Self-defense. You think a jury would convict?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你自己看着办{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Just do what you have to do.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我就当你同意了啊，警察到时会来抓你\N{\r英文}You know, I'm taking that as permission. The cops'll be coming after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.01,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}萨伦伯格没法赶来{\i}\N{\r英文}{\an8\i1}Sullenberger couldn't be here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.31,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我还真没见过这种场面{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I haven't seen anything like this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}在国家运输安全委员会的调查期间{\i}\N{\r英文}{\an8\i1}He is not able to speak to the media{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.10,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他们把整条街堵得水泄不通{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}They're blocking the entire street.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:27.00,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}他也不能接受媒体采访{\i}\N{\r英文}{\an8\i1}while the NTSB is conducting its investigation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.30,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}周围邻居都很生气{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}And the neighbours are furious.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:26.90,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他们也关心这件事，不过还是很生气{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Concerned, but furious.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.52,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利，你在听我说吗？\N{\r英文}Sully, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.80,中文,,0,0,0,,要不我们晚点再谈\N{\r英文}Maybe we should talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:36.00,中文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的，就是现在了，我等了一整天\N{\r英文}Honey, it is later. I've been waiting all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.32,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你没事吧？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Are you okay?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我没事，就是有点累，没别的了\N{\r英文}Yeah, just tired, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.40,中文,,0,0,0,,女儿都还好吧?\N{\r英文}How are the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.64,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}她们有点...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Well, they're...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:47.48,中文,,0,0,0,,她们有点不知所措，好像你也一样啊\N{\r英文}They're a little overwhelmed. It sounds like you are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.32,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯...\N{\r英文}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.88,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，她们会没事的\N{\r英文}Yeah, well, they'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.16,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}太多的关注了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It is a lot.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.60,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r英文}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.72,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这些丢失的发动机{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Those missing engines{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.56,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}肯定不是调查人员所希望的样子{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}were definitely not what investigators wanted.{\i} ..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在家喻户晓了\N{\r英文}The whole world is talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.80,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}老公大人{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}My Sully.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.88,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊，我真是不敢相信这一切\N{\r英文}God, I just can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.08,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}洛丽，我得在这多呆几天{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Lorrie, I have to stay here longer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.92,中文,,0,0,0,,配合国家运输安全委员会的调查\N{\r英文}for the NTSB investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:13.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我先前跟你说了吗？没的话，我向你道歉\N{\r英文}Did I tell you that already? I apologize if I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:18.57,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}没有什么需要你道歉的，你就在需要你的地方{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}There is no need for you to apologize. You are right where you need to be.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你明白，我做了该做的一切\N{\r英文}I want you to know, I did the best I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:29.88,中文,,0,0,0,,那还用说，你救了所有人\N{\r英文}Of course you did. You saved everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:35.57,中文,,0,0,0,,要不我们明天在说吧，我累了\N{\r英文}Uh, maybe we should just talk in the morning. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.32,中文,,0,0,0,,受到这样的关注，我真有点吃不消\N{\r英文}I'm overwhelmed by all this attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.76,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我明天要上电视了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I'm gonna be on TV in the morning.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.80,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他们会问我什么问题，我该如何应答？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}What are they gonna ask me? What am I gonna say?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.08,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利，你要我过去陪你吗？\N{\r英文}Sully, do you want me to come be with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.16,中文,,0,0,0,,不用，洛丽\N{\r英文}No, Lorrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.76,中文,,0,0,0,,谢了，可女儿还需要你\N{\r英文}Thanks, but the girls need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.24,中文,,0,0,0,,替我向她们问好\N{\r英文}Tell them I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:57.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你，睡个好觉\N{\r英文}I love you. Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.32,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.92,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，也许我一觉醒来，会是1月14号\N{\r英文}Hey, maybe when I wake up, it'll be January 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.24,中文,,0,0,0,,那样多好啊？\N{\r英文}Wouldn't that be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\r英文}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}机长萨伦伯格为什么要做出那个重大决定{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Why Captain Sullenberger made that fateful decision{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.52,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}把哈德逊河变为跑道？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}to turn the Hudson into a runway?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.33,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}只有他心知肚明{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Well, only he can answer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:24.12,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可我们现在知道那是错误的决定{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}But we now know it was the wrong choice.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:28.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是危及机上所有人性命的决定{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}A choice that endangered the lives of all of those onboard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:32.28,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}几乎整个国家都尊他为英雄{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}So, while much of the country hails him as a hero,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可新出炉的信息将肯定改变大众对于{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}this new information will certainly change everyone's understanding{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}“哈德逊奇迹”的见解{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}of the so-called "Miracle on the Hudson."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:45.12,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}“萨利”萨伦伯格，你是个英雄，还是个骗子？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Sully Sullenberger, are you a hero or a fraud?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.96,中文,,0,0,0,,- 喂？  - 杰夫？\N{\r英文}- Hello?  - Jeff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.68,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉这么晚还打给你\N{\r英文}I'm sorry to call so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}没事，我在这边也睡不着{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It's okay. There's no sleep in this room either.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.20,中文,,0,0,0,,这里的一块士力架要5块钱，你敢相信？\N{\r英文}Can you believe they charge $5 for a Snickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:18.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我要是多咬几口，航空公司怕是得破产\N{\r英文}I could bankrupt the airline in about four bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,就是看你想不想...\N{\r英文}Just thought maybe you would want to, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.08,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}谈谈？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Talk?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.60,中文,,0,0,0,,肯定的\N{\r英文}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.68,中文,,0,0,0,,出去透透气吧\N{\r英文}Let's get some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.40,中文,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\r英文}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.20,中文,,0,0,0,,好，5分钟后见\N{\r英文}All right. Be down there in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你还享受颤抖啊？\N{\r英文}You enjoying the shakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.17,中文,,0,0,0,,噩梦，心跳过快\N{\r英文}The nightmares, rapid heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.36,中文,,0,0,0,,有一点\N{\r英文}A little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.32,中文,,0,0,0,,工会建议我们接受心理咨询\N{\r英文}Union's offering us counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.52,中文,,0,0,0,,对，他们会怎么说?\N{\r英文}Yeah. What are they gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你的飞机坠毁了，你还活着\N{\r英文}"You were in a plane crash and lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.28,中文,,0,0,0,,这可能会留下点后遗症\N{\r英文}"It may have a minor impact on your day-to-day."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我讨厌失控的感觉\N{\r英文}I don't like not being in control of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.88,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我想回到原来的样子  - 是啊\N{\r英文}- I want my self back.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我只希望6个月后，我们能调侃\N{\r英文}I'm hoping six months from now, we'll just be laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.68,中文,,0,0,0,,自己上大卫·莱特曼晚间秀的事\N{\r英文}about how we got to meet David Letterman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要上大卫·莱特曼晚间秀？\N{\r英文}We're doing David Letterman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.36,中文,,0,0,0,,对，就在下一个国家运输安全委员会的问询后\N{\r英文}Yeah. Right after the next NTSB interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.60,中文,,0,0,0,,莱特曼\N{\r英文}Letterman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜大卫会多讲几个笑话的\N{\r英文}I'm guessing Dave is gonna be slightly funnier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.72,中文,,0,0,0,,真是像做梦一样\N{\r英文}This is so surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜自己快有点\N{\r英文}I guess I'm having a little trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.73,中文,,0,0,0,,分不清现实和这一摊子乌七八糟的事了\N{\r英文}separating reality from whatever the hell this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.04,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们两个大冷天的还得四处奔波\N{\r英文}This is two men freezing their asses off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利\N{\r英文}Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.56,中文,,0,0,0,,别担心，你做的事很了不起\N{\r英文}Don't worry. You did a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.88,中文,,0,0,0,,会被载入史册的\N{\r英文}It's gonna be remembered for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.76,中文,,0,0,0,,可滑稽的是\N{\r英文}Here's the funny thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我40年来运送了上百万的乘客\N{\r英文}I've delivered a million passengers over 40 years in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:43.09,中文,,0,0,0,,可到最后，208秒就给我盖棺定论了\N{\r英文}but in the end, I'm gonna be judged on 208 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.20,中文,,0,0,0,,别这样，明天会更好的\N{\r英文}Come on. Tomorrow's gonna be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:52.16,中文,,0,0,0,,计算机模拟会证明你是对的，我们都会重返驾驶舱的\N{\r英文}Computer sims will prove you were right. We can all put our wings back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你想跑会儿步吗？\N{\r英文}You wanna run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好，一起跑会儿吧\N{\r英文}Yeah, let's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.65,中文,,0,0,0,,真他妈冻死人了\N{\r英文}Fucking cold out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.76,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}很显然{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It was obvious.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.33,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}情况十分危急{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It was a critical situation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:08.92,中文,,0,0,0,,在那样的低空失去双发动力\N{\r英文}losing thrust in both engines at a low altitude
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:13.28,中文,,0,0,0,,底下就是地球上人口最密集的地区之一\N{\r英文}over one of the most densely populated areas of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:18.60,中文,,0,0,0,,可选择在哈德逊河上着陆，仍然是个很大的未知数\N{\r英文}But choosing to land on the Hudson, that was still a big "if."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我确信自己能办到\N{\r英文}I was sure I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:22.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你确信？\N{\r英文}You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.52,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:28.20,中文,,0,0,0,,听到别人喊你英雄，是什么感觉？\N{\r英文}How do you feel when people call you a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我不觉得自己像英雄\N{\r英文}I don't feel like a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.96,中文,,0,0,0,,和别人一样，我只是做好本职工作而已\N{\r英文}I'm just a man who was doing his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.88,中文,,0,0,0,,是恰当的人在需要的时候力挽狂澜\N{\r英文}The right man for the job at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:42.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你飞行了有将近40年了？\N{\r英文}You've been flying for what, nearly 40 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.01,中文,,0,0,0,,42年，干了一辈子\N{\r英文}Forty-two. It's been my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我的整个人生\N{\r英文}My whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你来操纵\N{\r英文}Your aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我来操纵\N{\r英文}My aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.52,中文,,0,0,0,,余下的夏天，我都要忙着开轻型机喷洒农药\N{\r英文}I'll be busy crop dusting in the Super Cub rest of the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.33,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，你想什么时候飞都行\N{\r英文}So, you can take the plane up, I guess, when you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.60,中文,,0,0,0,,还是6元一小时，就当作是训练课吧\N{\r英文}Still six bucks an hour. I'll consider it lesson time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,飞行员要热爱学习\N{\r英文}A pilot never stops acquiring knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你总会犯错，人之常情，汲取教训就是了\N{\r英文}You'll make mistakes, everyone does. Just learn from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.85,中文,,0,0,0,,明白，教官\N{\r英文}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.84,中文,,0,0,0,,要切记的是，不管遇到什么状况\N{\r英文}And never forget, no matter what's happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.52,中文,,0,0,0,,操纵好飞机\N{\r英文}to fly the airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.80,中文,,0,0,0,,完全明白，教官\N{\r英文}Absolutely, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.28,中文,,0,0,0,,还有一件事，挺重要的\N{\r英文}Oh, one other thing, and this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,- 教官？  - 要笑口常开\N{\r英文}- Sir?  - You can go ahead and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.40,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\r英文}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.37,中文,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉我出了不少汗  - 不用\N{\r英文}- I apologize for the perspiration.  - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你完成了那样的壮举\N{\r英文}After what you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我相信凯蒂不会咄咄逼人的\N{\r英文}I'd think that Katie couldn't be too intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是怕凯蒂\N{\r英文}Oh, it wasn't Katie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.21,中文,,0,0,0,,是因为她带来的这些灯光和摄像机\N{\r英文}It was the lights and the camera that she brought with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.16,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，化妆完毕\N{\r英文}Okay. All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.44,中文,,0,0,0,,这一下是替我妈\N{\r英文}That was from my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.72,中文,,0,0,0,,她叫布兰达\N{\r英文}Her name is Brenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.64,中文,,0,0,0,,她让我跟你说声谢谢，还有她是单身\N{\r英文}she says to say "thank you" and that she's single.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.24,中文,,0,0,0,,跟布兰达说声谢谢，可我家里有媳妇等着呢\N{\r英文}Well, you tell Brenda thank you, but I've got a girl at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.44,中文,,0,0,0,,- 她真幸运  - 谢谢\N{\r英文}- Lucky woman.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.69,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利\N{\r英文}Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.92,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}萨利，萨利！{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Sully. Sully!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.64,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利，你神游到哪去了？\N{\r英文}Sully, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我站在这叫你都不答应\N{\r英文}I'm standing here calling your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你到底怎么了？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}What's up with you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你得专注起来\N{\r英文}You need to get focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.29,中文,,0,0,0,,媒体邀约可是源源不断在涌来啊\N{\r英文}Because the media request avalanche continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.68,中文,,0,0,0,,好，好的\N{\r英文}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.12,中文,,0,0,0,,拉里·鲁尼自告奋勇\N{\r英文}Larry Rooney volunteered to jump in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.32,中文,,0,0,0,,要来给你保驾护航\N{\r英文}and ride shotgun with you the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.65,中文,,0,0,0,,想你可能需要个朋友\N{\r英文}Thought you might need a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.96,中文,,0,0,0,,他会接你去今天的国家运输安全委员会的会议\N{\r英文}He'll take you to today's NTSB meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.33,中文,,0,0,0,,空客也完成了他们的计算机模拟\N{\r英文}Airbus completed their computer simulations as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,好，很好，那是好事\N{\r英文}Good. Good, that'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.60,中文,,0,0,0,,另外还有，阿尼·金泰尔打了电话\N{\r英文}There's something else. Arnie Gentile called.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.65,中文,,0,0,0,,他拿到了飞机通信寻址与报告系统的数据\N{\r英文}He has the ACARS data.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:45.16,中文,,0,0,0,,显示左翼发动机维持在空转状态\N{\r英文}The left engine was still operating at idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:48.32,中文,,0,0,0,,不可能，我感觉它完了\N{\r英文}Not possible. I felt it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就像在半空中停住了一样\N{\r英文}It was like we were stopped in midair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.92,中文,,0,0,0,,阿尼说也有可能是在次空转\N{\r英文}Arnie said there was a chance it was sub-idle,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这样的话就仍有推力\N{\r英文}that it still could've had thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:58.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是让你有个准备，因为国家运输安全委员会也已得知了\N{\r英文}I'm just letting you know since the NTSB already does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.24,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r英文}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你打算退休吗？\N{\r英文}ls retirement next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你接下来做什么？有什么打算？\N{\r英文}What's next for you? What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.52,中文,,0,0,0,,请让开点\N{\r英文}Some room, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.21,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}萨利，到这边来{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Sully! Over here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.92,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，拉里，真高兴能见到个熟人\N{\r英文}Hey, Larry. Good to see a friendly face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你今天也就只能见到这一张了\N{\r英文}Might be the last one you see today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你不是开玩笑吧，还要让我们再来一遍？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}You've got to be kidding me. We've been through all this before.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.97,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我并无意想惹恼你{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Look, I'm sorry if you're frustrated,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:34.16,中文,,0,0,0,,可我们的工作就是去调查飞机掉进哈德逊河的原因\N{\r英文}but ourjob is to investigate how a plane ended up in the Hudson River.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.00,中文,,0,0,0,,是浮在哈德逊河上\N{\r英文}On the Hudson River.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.85,中文,,0,0,0,,今年这个时候去“钓鱼”是不是早了点？\N{\r英文}Isn't it a little early in the year to go fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.52,中文,,0,0,0,,寻求事实跟“钓鱼”完全是两码事，斯基尔斯先生\N{\r英文}Seeking the facts is hardly "fishing," Mr. Skiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.12,中文,,0,0,0,,那好吧，我告诉你个最重要的事实\N{\r英文}Okay, then here's the most important fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.60,中文,,0,0,0,,当天只有两个人知道驾驶舱内发生的情况\N{\r英文}There's only two people who know what happened in the cockpit that day
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.80,中文,,0,0,0,,而我就是其中之一\N{\r英文}and I'm one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我们感谢你分享自己的见解\N{\r英文}And we appreciate your perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你可知道我们今天来的原因？\N{\r英文}Why do you even think we're here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:00.00,中文,,0,0,0,,是因为机长萨伦伯格没有返回拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}It's because Captain Sullenberger did not head back to LaGuardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我才刚完成A320的训练，我可以向你们担保\N{\r英文}Look, ljust finished training on the A320 and I can tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.72,中文,,0,0,0,,飞机能在我们的操纵下成功迫降\N{\r英文}the only reason the plane operated as well as it did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:08.45,中文,,0,0,0,,能有地点选择降落的唯一原因\N{\r英文}that the aircraft could land anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.24,中文,,0,0,0,,是因为机长萨伦伯格打开了辅助动力装置\N{\r英文}is because Captain Sullenberger turned on the Auxiliary Power Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.52,中文,,0,0,0,,他不过是执行快速检查单的要求而已\N{\r英文}He was simply following the QRH.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.17,中文,,0,0,0,,不，不是，他并没这样\N{\r英文}No. No, he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.12,中文,,0,0,0,,他根本没有走正常程序\N{\r英文}He wasn't following proper procedure at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我当时就拿着快速检查单，所以我知道\N{\r英文}And I know, because I had the QRH in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.56,中文,,0,0,0,,发动机刚减速，他就打开了辅助动力装置\N{\r英文}He switched on the APU immediately after engine rollback.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,而根据空客的检查单，那是要做的第15件事\N{\r英文}According to Airbus, that's the 15th thing on the list to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.05,中文,,0,0,0,,第15件\N{\r英文}Fifteenth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.89,中文,,0,0,0,,他要是执行那破单子，我们早完蛋了\N{\r英文}If he had followed the damn rules, we'd all be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.80,中文,,0,0,0,,或许你们不爽的就是这点？\N{\r英文}Maybe that's the part you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不习惯别人点醒你们\N{\r英文}You're not used to having answers to your guesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:39.84,中文,,0,0,0,,杰夫想说的是\N{\r英文}Look, what Jeff is saying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:44.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我熟悉A320，知道它的长处和短板\N{\r英文}is that I know the A320, what it does and what it doesn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:48.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我读过无数牺牲机长的驾驶舱通话录音副本\N{\r英文}I have read countless CVR transcripts of deceased pilots
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.81,中文,,0,0,0,,也有相当多的事故调查经验\N{\r英文}and I have significant accident investigation experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.24,中文,,0,0,0,,没人质疑这点\N{\r英文}There is no question
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:57.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你是个天资卓越、爱岗敬业和经验丰富的专业人才\N{\r英文}that you are a talented, dedicated, experienced professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.36,中文,,0,0,0,,1月15号前你飞过的所有航班\N{\r英文}But all the flights you piloted before January 15th
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:03.88,中文,,0,0,0,,之前你调查过的任何事故，都与这起调查无关\N{\r英文}and every crash you investigated are not the purview of this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:07.04,中文,,0,0,0,,今天我们只关心全美航空1549\N{\r英文}Only US Airways 1549 matters today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你们的工会已被告知\N{\r英文}Your union has been advised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.28,中文,,0,0,0,,飞机通信寻址与报告系统的传输数据显示\N{\r英文}ACARS data relayed that the left engine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.32,中文,,0,0,0,,左翼发动机在整个飞行期间一直在转动\N{\r英文}continued to turn throughout the flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.09,中文,,0,0,0,,那飞机通信寻址与报告系统的数据错了\N{\r英文}Then the ACARS data is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.92,中文,,0,0,0,,记录显示就在鸟击过后\N{\r英文}The evidence shows that the left engine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:22.36,中文,,0,0,0,,左翼发动机在空转或次空转状态\N{\r英文}was at idle or sub-idle immediately following the bird strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:25.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你把左翼发动机找来，我就给你看死鸟和停车的痕迹\N{\r英文}You show me the left engine, I'll show you dead birds and no power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:30.28,中文,,0,0,0,,左翼发动机在坠机过程中，因水面撞击而丢失\N{\r英文}The left engine was lost in the crash due to excessive damage on touchdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.64,中文,,0,0,0,,不过我们可以以后再研究这个问题\N{\r英文}But we can circle back to that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就先假定你说的是事实\N{\r英文}Let's just assume that it was, as you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.36,中文,,0,0,0,,因鸟击造成双发停车\N{\r英文}a dual engine loss due to bird strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:41.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你飞机的重量是68.7吨\N{\r英文}Your weight was 151 ,510 pounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:44.68,中文,,0,0,0,,风向和温度分别是西北偏北和零下6度\N{\r英文}wind and temperature north, northwest, 21°.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:48.08,中文,,0,0,0,,速度和高度分别是370公里/小时和859米\N{\r英文}Speed and altitude 200 knots at 2,818 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.29,中文,,0,0,0,,- 对吗？  - 对\N{\r英文}- Agree?  - Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:52.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们用各种算法同时进行演算\N{\r英文}We were able to run all the algorithms concurrently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:57.12,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549次航班的计算机模拟结果\N{\r英文}And the resulting computer simulations of US Airways Flight 1549
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:21:00.09,中文,,0,0,0,,显示航空工程师是对的\N{\r英文}show that the aviation engineers were correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,在鸟击过后，飞机有足够的高度和速度\N{\r英文}There was enough altitude and speed after the bird strike
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.96,中文,,0,0,0,,可以成功返回拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}for a successful return to LaGuardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:07.88,中文,,0,0,0,,成功返回？\N{\r英文}Successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:10.40,中文,,0,0,0,,飞机降落在拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}The plane landed at LaGuardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:11.88,中文,,0,0,0,,完好无缺\N{\r英文}Intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:13.96,中文,,0,0,0,,未有损坏\N{\r英文}Undamaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个计算机模拟给的结果？\N{\r英文}You got that from one computer simulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.36,中文,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\r英文}BEN: NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:18.68,中文,,0,0,0,,20个\N{\r英文}From 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,包括一次尝试降落在泰特伯勒机场的跑道19\N{\r英文}Including attempts made for Teterboro runways 1-9
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.68,中文,,0,0,0,,拉瓜迪亚的跑道22和跑道13\N{\r英文}and LaGuardia runways 2-2 and 1-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:29.52,中文,,0,0,0,,每个计算机模拟都使用同样的飞行参数\N{\r英文}Every computer simulation with the exact flight parameters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:33.12,中文,,0,0,0,,证明返回拉瓜迪亚机场是可能的\N{\r英文}demonstrated that a return to LaGuardia was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.88,中文,,0,0,0,,而且不只是可能，是可行的\N{\r英文}And notjust possible, probable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.04,中文,,0,0,0,,有谁还想听更多的计算机模拟结果？\N{\r英文}Does anyone need to hear further computer evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.36,中文,,0,0,0,,机长萨伦伯格?\N{\r英文}Captain Sullenberger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:48.80,中文,,0,0,0,,副驾驶斯基尔斯？\N{\r英文}First Officer Skiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.76,中文,,0,0,0,,这次就算了\N{\r英文}Not at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:55.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我想再核实下计算机模拟用的参数\N{\r英文}I would like to go over the parameters that were used.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会给工会提供的\N{\r英文}We will make them available to the union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:21:59.56,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:01.52,中文,,0,0,0,,调查一旦完成\N{\r英文}Once the investigation is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们将公开具体的计算机模拟结果\N{\r英文}we'll be able to share the actual computer simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:06.44,中文,,0,0,0,,目前数据暂时保密\N{\r英文}For now, they remain confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:08.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还不能向媒体披露\N{\r英文}We cannot afford a leak to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:12.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这件事受到的关注实在是太大了\N{\r英文}There's been far too much talk in the press already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.61,中文,,0,0,0,,等完整的驾驶舱通话记录导出\N{\r英文}When the complete cockpit voice recording is compiled,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.96,中文,,0,0,0,,以及空管和机上的通讯整理完成\N{\r英文}along with ATC and all onboard transcripts combined,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我们再通知你们\N{\r英文}we will call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:28.48,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢各位，再见\N{\r英文}Thank you, gentlemen. Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.12,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:40.72,中文,,0,0,0,,他们像是在玩“吃豆人”\N{\r英文}They're playing Pacman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.49,中文,,0,0,0,,而你是给大活人开飞机啊\N{\r英文}You were flying a plane full of human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:47.60,中文,,0,0,0,,奇怪，这跟我的记忆完全对不上\N{\r英文}Somehow, that's not how I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:49.57,中文,,0,0,0,,就觉着不对劲啊\N{\r英文}It just doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:51.76,中文,,0,0,0,,因为就是不对啊\N{\r英文}It's because it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:54.44,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利，你使出了浑身解数，要求不能再高了\N{\r英文}Sully, you did everything you could and it was more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:56.73,中文,,0,0,0,,去问问乘客\N{\r英文}Ask the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:59.16,中文,,0,0,0,,问问你的老婆和孩子，问问我的家人\N{\r英文}Ask your wife and kids. Ask mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,那你从驾驶舱听到的第一句话是什么?\N{\r英文}So what was the first thing you heard from the cockpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.68,中文,,0,0,0,,- 准备紧急撞击姿势，就是这句  - 准备紧急撞击姿势\N{\r英文}-"Brace for impact." Yes.  -"Brace for impact."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.60,中文,,0,0,0,,以前从驾驶舱里听到过吗？\N{\r英文}Now, uh, ever hear that before coming out of a cockpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.21,中文,,0,0,0,,没，从没有过\N{\r英文}No, not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:39.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那你平常生活中有听到过吗？\N{\r英文}Ever hear that in any other aspect of your lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:44.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的\N{\r英文}{\i1}I don't know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:46.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的\N{\r英文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.12,0:23:52.72,中文,,0,0,0,,他们说不定会让我滚蛋\N{\r英文}They could take this show away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:56.56,中文,,0,0,0,,杰夫很放松，应对自如\N{\r英文}Jeff was relaxed and funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:58.76,中文,,0,0,0,,接下来的采访应该都会找他了\N{\r英文}He should be getting all of our interview requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:00.16,中文,,0,0,0,,他们有给你报酬吗？\N{\r英文}{\i1}Are they paying you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,至少上媒体这种应该有吧？\N{\r英文}for all this media stuff at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:03.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}新闻节目，洛丽 {\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It's news, Lorrie.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:05.61,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是没有报酬拿的{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}No payment is necessary.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:07.60,中文,,0,0,0,,要是银行也这么想就好了\N{\r英文}Oh, I wish the bank felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.16,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么，你这是什么意思？\N{\r英文}Why? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:10.56,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就是...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It's just...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:15.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我们又收到催款通知了，布尤特县的那块空地\N{\r英文}We got another notice about the space in Butte County.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.24,0:24:19.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会找到租户的\N{\r英文}We'll find a tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:20.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就是需要时间{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It just takes time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:22.65,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊，这句话你都说了8个月了，萨利\N{\r英文}Yeah, you've been saying that for nine months, Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.80,0:24:23.88,中文,,0,0,0,,可它还是空着\N{\r英文}It's still vacant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:25.72,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}经济肯定会回暖的{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}The economy has to take a turn.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.20,0:24:30.96,中文,,0,0,0,,可是，如果我们失去那块地，马上就会牵连到我们的房子\N{\r英文}It feels like if we lose that space, the next domino to fall is the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.60,0:24:34.00,中文,,0,0,0,,洛丽，我们不会失去房子的\N{\r英文}Lorrie, we're not gonna lose the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:35.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}对不起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I'm sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.80,0:24:37.29,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\r英文}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.48,0:24:39.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我有点烦躁\N{\r英文}I'm just anxious
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.48,0:24:41.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我独自一人，而且睡眠不足\N{\r英文}and I'm alone and not enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.24,0:24:43.24,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嗯，我明白{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Yeah, I know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.44,0:24:45.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我在这里也睡不好觉\N{\r英文}Not a lot of sleep going on here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.76,0:24:47.60,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}对不起，我又让你更焦虑了吧{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I'm sorry if I'm adding to your stress.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.76,0:24:50.16,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你知道自己多快能回去工作吗？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}But just tell me you'll be back in the air soon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.72,0:24:53.64,中文,,0,0,0,,那要等到国家运输安全委员会完成他们的调查了\N{\r英文}Not until the NTSB is finished with their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.40,0:24:55.81,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们家需要你工作{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We need you flying.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.96,0:24:58.93,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}洛丽，如果情况急转直下{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Lorrie, if this goes badly,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.08,0:25:04.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我作为安全专家的事业，会连同网站和生意一同消失\N{\r英文}my career as a safety expert will end as a website and a business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.24,0:25:06.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我更在乎的是你机长的事业\N{\r英文}I'm more worried about your career as a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.60,0:25:12.60,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我这次真搞砸了\N{\r英文}What if I did blow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.00,0:25:14.65,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你说什么？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}What are you saying?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.52,0:25:19.16,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我这次真弄错了，晚节不保？\N{\r英文}What if I did get this wrong, so close to the end of my career?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.92,0:25:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我真危及了机上全体乘客的性命？\N{\r英文}If I endangered the lives of all those passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.64,0:25:28.36,中文,,0,0,0,,萨利，看看新闻，你成了英雄\N{\r英文}Sully, watch the news. You're a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.52,0:25:31.12,中文,,0,0,0,,每个人都要对此习以为常，包括国家运输安全委员会\N{\r英文}Everyone's gonna have to get used to it, including the NTSB.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.60,0:25:34.28,中文,,0,0,0,,最糟的情形\N{\r英文}Worst case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.44,0:25:37.17,中文,,0,0,0,,国家运输安全委员会有合理根据定我的罪\N{\r英文}the NTSB lists me as the probable cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.32,0:25:39.97,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是立即退休，退休金也没了\N{\r英文}That's immediate retirement. No pension.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.64,0:25:41.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我一生的事业付之一炬\N{\r英文}My life's work gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.84,0:25:44.96,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，你吓到我了，萨利，到底怎么回事？\N{\r英文}Okay, you're scaring me now, Sully. What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.72,0:25:49.00,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}左翼发动机有可能一直在空转{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}The left engine might have still been idling.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.20,0:25:51.88,中文,,0,0,0,,而且空客的模拟显示\N{\r英文}And the Airbus simulations say
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:25:55.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以安全返回拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}I could've made it back to LaGuardia safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.56,0:25:57.21,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可那根本没道理啊{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}But that doesn't make sense.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.68,0:26:01.65,中文,,0,0,0,,和我在驾驶舱的亲身感受完全不一致\N{\r英文}Doesn't jibe with everything I felt in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.36,0:26:04.52,中文,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要那样做，萨利？\N{\r英文}Then why did you do it, Sully?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.72,0:26:07.48,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么要在水上降落？\N{\r英文}What, land in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.48,0:26:10.92,中文,,0,0,0,,没有比那更危险的事了\N{\r英文}Wasn't that the most dangerous thing you could have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.92,0:26:16.22,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8}欢迎来到拉瓜迪亚机场
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:20.68,中文,,0,0,0,,下午好，古里斯曼女士\N{\r英文}Good afternoon, Gursimran.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.84,0:26:24.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你推荐金枪鱼罗勒三明治还是火腿干酪三明治？\N{\r英文}The, uh, tuna basil or the ham and cheddar?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.08,0:26:27.56,中文,,0,0,0,,金枪鱼罗勒三明治，萨利机长，非常新鲜\N{\r英文}Tuna basil, Mr. Sully. Very fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.16,0:26:33.08,中文,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 注意安全\N{\r英文}- Thank you.  - Be careful up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.24,0:26:35.20,中文,,0,0,0,,今天太冷，冻死了\N{\r英文}Too cold today. Too much cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.40,0:26:37.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你什么时候跟我一起飞行啊？\N{\r英文}When are you gonna come fly with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.92,0:26:40.84,中文,,0,0,0,,等全美航空开通到海德拉巴的航线再说吧\N{\r英文}When US Air starts flights to Hyderabad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.20,0:26:44.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我会跟董事长提议的，看能否被公司采纳\N{\r英文}I will talk to the chairman, see what we can work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.52,0:26:48.60,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}看在老天的份上{\i}  {\i1}不行{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Oh, for heaven's sakes, Diane!{\i}  {\i1}No!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.76,0:26:50.44,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是他的生日啊  - 不行，老妈\N{\r英文}- It's his birthday!  - Come on! No, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:52.04,中文,,0,0,0,,给他买点什么吧\N{\r英文}Just a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.20,0:26:54.40,中文,,0,0,0,,行李箱里已经塞满了给威尔的礼物\N{\r英文}The suitcase is already overstuffed with gifts for Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.56,0:26:56.48,中文,,0,0,0,,在机场买东西总是乐趣多多\N{\r英文}It's always fun to get something from the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.76,0:26:58.52,中文,,0,0,0,,有种旅游的感觉\N{\r英文}Feels like you've traveled, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.72,0:27:00.44,中文,,0,0,0,,老妈，他才满1岁\N{\r英文}Ma, he's turning one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.60,0:27:03.36,中文,,0,0,0,,别以为他分得清礼物是哪买的\N{\r英文}Don't think he'll be discerning what gift came from where.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.52,0:27:04.93,中文,,0,0,0,,可我知道\N{\r英文}But I Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.08,0:27:06.96,中文,,0,0,0,,买个雪景球如何\N{\r英文}Maybe a snow globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.12,0:27:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,他会记得的礼物，有纽约标志的\N{\r英文}Something he'll remember. Something "New York."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.80,0:27:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我们小时候你有这么大方吗？\N{\r英文}Were you this generous when we were kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.20,0:27:13.40,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，宝贝\N{\r英文}Okay, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.56,0:27:15.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我也给你买个雪景球\N{\r英文}I'll get you a snow globe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.32,0:27:19.04,中文,,0,0,0,,好，走吧\N{\r英文}Fine. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.76,0:27:32.60,中文,,0,0,0,,- 下午好，希拉  - 机长好\N{\r英文}- Good afternoon, Sheila.  - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.92,0:27:36.25,中文,,0,0,0,,- 嗨，多琳，堂娜  - 机长\N{\r英文}- Hello, Donna.  - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.40,0:27:38.36,中文,,0,0,0,,- 杰夫  - 嘿，萨利，你好啊\N{\r英文}- Jeff.  - Hey, Sully. How are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.20,0:27:44.40,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，听我说，杰夫！\N{\r英文}Hey. guys! Jeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.60,0:27:45.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们肯定赶不上了\N{\r英文}We're not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.92,0:27:47.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我为这次旅行准备了一年，老爸\N{\r英文}I've been waiting for a year for this trip, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.24,0:27:49.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我们才不会错过航班的，我们登机口见，好吗？\N{\r英文}I'm not gonna miss this flight. Just meet us at the gate, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.64,0:27:51.29,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}待会见，罗比叔叔{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We'll see you there, Uncle Robbie.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.76,0:27:55.96,中文,,0,0,0,,高度表校正，30.23英吋汞柱\N{\r英文}Altimeter is verified. 3-0-2-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.12,0:27:58.28,中文,,0,0,0,,30.23英吋汞柱\N{\r英文}3-0-2-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.56,0:28:03.44,中文,,0,0,0,,起飞检查单确认完毕\N{\r英文}Start checklist complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.92,0:28:08.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你真认为他们会放行？\N{\r英文}You really think they'll release us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.60,0:28:10.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我看了最新的预报\N{\r英文}I've checked the latest reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.92,0:28:12.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我们到夏洛特是畅通无阻的\N{\r英文}We're clear all the way to Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.12,0:28:15.28,中文,,0,0,0,,那去吃牛排吧\N{\r英文}Then steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:17.16,中文,,0,0,0,,德尔·弗雷斯科餐馆，我请\N{\r英文}Del Frisco's. On me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.48,0:28:18.81,中文,,0,0,0,,从没去过\N{\r英文}Never been.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.12,0:28:20.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不过听人夸过\N{\r英文}And I hear good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.52,0:28:21.52,中文,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\r英文}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.60,0:28:24.25,中文,,0,0,0,,肋眼牛排会让你爱到心碎的\N{\r英文}The rib eye'll break your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.44,0:28:26.96,中文,,0,0,0,,其实我更偏爱T骨排\N{\r英文}I'm more of a porterhouse man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.64,0:28:29.92,中文,,0,0,0,,吃T骨排会让你心梗的\N{\r英文}The porterhouse will stop your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.60,0:28:32.72,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空飞往夏洛特的1549号航班{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We are now closed for US Airways flight 1549,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:33.80,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}停止售票{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}service to Charlotte...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.96,0:28:34.96,中文,,0,0,0,,等等，等等\N{\r英文}Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:36.45,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你快点  - 等等，等等\N{\r英文}- You got it.  - Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.96,0:28:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨，抱歉了\N{\r英文}Hi. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.64,0:28:39.97,中文,,0,0,0,,是精神航空让我们过来的\N{\r英文}Um, Spirit sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.12,0:28:41.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的航班取消了，他们说这可以转机\N{\r英文}We got canceled and they said that we were re-routed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.12,0:28:43.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你们这还有空位吗？\N{\r英文}That you guys had some seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.60,0:28:44.64,中文,,0,0,0,,停止售票了\N{\r英文}Flight is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.80,0:28:47.32,中文,,0,0,0,,等等，你看见那边一瘸一拐的老头了吗？\N{\r英文}Wait, see that old guy limping up right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.48,0:28:49.64,中文,,0,0,0,,那是我爸，有要紧事，他必须得赶上这班飞机\N{\r英文}That's my dad. It's an emergency. He's gotta be on this flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.80,0:28:51.48,中文,,0,0,0,,什么要紧事？\N{\r英文}What kind of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.64,0:28:54.29,中文,,0,0,0,,- 打高尔夫  - 航班取消了？\N{\r英文}- Golf emergency.  - This flight canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.44,0:28:55.80,中文,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\r英文}Oughta be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.68,0:28:58.33,中文,,0,0,0,,- 请把证件给我  - 太好了\N{\r英文}- ID's please.  - Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.48,0:28:59.48,中文,,0,0,0,,买几张票？\N{\r英文}How many people are traveling?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.64,0:29:00.80,中文,,0,0,0,,三张，谢谢\N{\r英文}Three. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.96,0:29:02.48,中文,,0,0,0,,没有连座了\N{\r英文}Nothing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.64,0:29:04.32,中文,,0,0,0,,没关系，让我坐机翼都行\N{\r英文}That's all right. Hell, I'll fly on the wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.72,0:29:06.84,中文,,0,0,0,,票拿好\N{\r英文}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.00,0:29:08.28,中文,,0,0,0,,22排A座\N{\r英文}22A,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.44,0:29:09.48,中文,,0,0,0,,6排A座\N{\r英文}6A
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.88,0:29:11.12,中文,,0,0,0,,还有6排C座\N{\r英文}and 6C.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.28,0:29:12.64,中文,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢，非常感谢  - 谢谢\N{\r英文}- Thank you. Thank you so much.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.84,0:29:13.84,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.00,0:29:16.12,中文,,0,0,0,,- 太好了  - 快乐收场\N{\r英文}- Yes! What! - Happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.52,0:29:19.00,中文,,0,0,0,,- 她对我“放电”了  - 你个风骚男\N{\r英文}- She gave me the eye.  - You charming bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.16,0:29:20.36,中文,,0,0,0,,欢迎登机\N{\r英文}Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.52,0:29:21.52,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你好啊  - 欢迎赶上末班车\N{\r英文}- How's it going?  - Lucky you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.68,0:29:22.96,中文,,0,0,0,,- - 嗯，就是  - 是啊\N{\r英文}- Yeah, no kidding.  - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.12,0:29:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢，借过   - 谢谢\N{\r英文}- Thank you. Sorry.  - Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.48,0:29:26.68,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们坐6排，杰夫  - 不是，吉米坐那\N{\r英文}- We're in six, Jeff.  - Oh, no. That's all Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.84,0:29:28.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我昨晚熬到3点，得补会儿觉\N{\r英文}I was up till 3:00. I gotta get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.68,0:29:29.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以睡这里啊\N{\r英文}You can sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:31.84,中文,,0,0,0,,算了吧，你一路上肯定会说个不停的高尔夫\N{\r英文}Not with you verbally running the course the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.04,0:29:33.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我想用7号铁头球棒来打第九洞\N{\r英文}"I think I'll play the seven iron on the 9th."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.92,0:29:35.28,中文,,0,0,0,,免了，再见\N{\r英文}No. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.08,0:29:39.73,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉，借个过\N{\r英文}Sorry. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.12,0:29:44.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我来帮你\N{\r英文}Here. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.88,0:29:46.53,中文,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 不客气\N{\r英文}- Thanks.  - Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.08,0:29:50.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你们好，让我进去一下\N{\r英文}Hey, guys, I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.72,0:29:51.80,中文,,0,0,0,,真抱歉\N{\r英文}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.96,0:29:53.20,中文,,0,0,0,,他就喜欢乱扔东西\N{\r英文}He likes to throw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.36,0:29:55.36,中文,,0,0,0,,那刚好，我喜欢接东西\N{\r英文}That's perfect. I like to catch everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.28,0:29:57.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你好啊，小家伙\N{\r英文}Hey, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.08,0:29:59.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我昨晚在google里搜了你\N{\r英文}I googled you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.12,0:30:03.32,中文,,0,0,0,,在你网站上看了下你公司的介绍\N{\r英文}Read all about your company on your website.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.64,0:30:05.72,中文,,0,0,0,,真是让人佩服啊\N{\r英文}It's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.44,0:30:07.44,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.24,0:30:12.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为自己很能吹牛呢，可跟你比？\N{\r英文}I thought I was a good bullshitter, but you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.84,0:30:13.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以以此谋生了\N{\r英文}You could go pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.16,0:30:15.16,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\r英文}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.32,0:30:16.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是开玩笑\N{\r英文}Oh, I'm only teasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.08,0:30:18.16,中文,,0,0,0,,不过你的网站的确让人以为\N{\r英文}The site does make it sound
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.32,0:30:20.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你的航空安全咨询公司有着上百名员工\N{\r英文}like your air safety consulting business has got about 100 employees
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.08,0:30:24.12,中文,,0,0,0,,在三个州都有总部\N{\r英文}and headquarters in three states.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.28,0:30:25.64,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我又仔细看了看\N{\r英文}Then when I dug a little deeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.84,0:30:28.24,中文,,0,0,0,,才意识到只有你一人\N{\r英文}I realized it's only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.12,0:30:30.45,中文,,0,0,0,,慢慢来嘛\N{\r英文}Go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.64,0:30:32.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我也是才创业\N{\r英文}I'm just getting it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.24,0:30:34.96,中文,,0,0,0,,很少有人会指责我吹牛\N{\r英文}I'm not usually accused of being a bullshitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.76,0:30:37.76,中文,,0,0,0,,别误会，其实我是表扬你\N{\r英文}Don't get me wrong. Actually, it's a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.92,0:30:40.76,中文,,0,0,0,,有没有网站，我都雇你\N{\r英文}Off that website? I'd hire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.92,0:30:42.92,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}下午好，女士们先生们{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Good afternoon, ladies and gentlemen.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.08,0:30:45.32,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}欢迎乘坐全美航空飞往夏洛特的{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Welcome onboard US Airways Flight 1549{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.48,0:30:46.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}1549号航班{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}with service to Charlotte.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.00,0:30:50.08,中文,,0,0,0,,请阅读你面前座椅后背口袋里的安全手册\N{\r英文}Please review the safety instruction card in the seatback pocket in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.28,0:30:52.60,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}里面介绍了飞机上的安全设施{\i}\N{\r英文}It explains the safety features of this aircraft
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.76,0:30:56.04,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}以及逃生出口和逃生路线，还有救生设备{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}as well as the location and operation of the exit and flotation devices.{\i}
