Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.96,0:31:02.20,中文,,0,0,0,,拉瓜迪亚停机坪，这是全美航空1549，准备从21号廊桥推开\N{\r英文}LaGuardia ramp, Cactus 1549. Ready for pushback at gate 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.36,0:31:04.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549，可以从21号廊桥推开{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Cactus 1549, gate 21 cleared to push.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.52,0:31:05.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}请滑行到等待位置28{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Spot 28, ground for taxi.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.36,0:31:15.12,中文,,0,0,0,,记得把它关掉\N{\r英文}Be sure you turn that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.44,0:31:17.80,中文,,0,0,0,,小桌板收起\N{\r英文}Tray table up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.84,0:31:38.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我就希望能从拉瓜迪亚准时起飞一次\N{\r英文}Just once I'd like to get out of LaGuardia on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.68,0:31:41.16,中文,,0,0,0,,想从拉瓜迪亚准时起飞只有一个办法，你知道吧\N{\r英文}Well, you know the only way to get out of LaGuardia on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.32,0:31:42.52,中文,,0,0,0,,什么办法？\N{\r英文}Yeah, What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.68,0:31:44.84,中文,,0,0,0,,飞肯尼迪机场啊\N{\r英文}Fly out of JFK.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.00,0:31:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,真好笑\N{\r英文}Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.52,0:31:57.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}起飞最低燃油检查{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Takeoff minimum fuel quantity verify.{\i}
