Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.84,0:32:00.17,中文,,0,0,0,,实载9888公斤\N{\r英文}We got 21.8 onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.32,0:32:03.05,中文,,0,0,0,,应载燃油8618公斤，实载9888公斤\N{\r英文}19,000 pounds required. 21.8 onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.20,0:32:06.24,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549，跑道4，可以起飞{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Cactus 1549. Runway 4. Cleared for takeoff.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.92,0:32:09.00,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549，可以起飞\N{\r英文}Cactus 1549. Cleared for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.48,0:32:16.84,中文,,0,0,0,,最大推力\N{\r英文}TO/GA.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.00,0:32:18.36,中文,,0,0,0,,检查了\N{\r英文}TO/GA set.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.04,0:32:43.16,中文,,0,0,0,,正上升\N{\r英文}Positive rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.76,0:32:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,抬轮\N{\r英文}Gear up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.68,0:32:47.68,中文,,0,0,0,,抬轮\N{\r英文}Gear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:32:59.89,中文,,0,0,0,,哈德逊河真美啊\N{\r英文}Nice view of the Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.68,0:33:03.44,中文,,0,0,0,,这下面的美景真是百看不厌\N{\r英文}I'll never get over how beautiful it is up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.28,0:33:06.16,中文,,0,0,0,,云端的生活更自在\N{\r英文}Life's easier in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.32,0:33:08.00,中文,,0,0,0,,是这样\N{\r英文}I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.44,0:33:11.44,中文,,0,0,0,,鸟群\N{\r英文}Birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.04,0:33:13.04,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\r英文}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.24,0:33:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\r英文}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.44,0:33:23.48,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.84,0:33:31.52,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可能是遇到紊流了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It's just turbulence, probably.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.68,0:33:32.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我去查看一下{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I'll check the cabin.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.48,0:33:34.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得是什么情况？\N{\r英文}What do you think's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:37.76,中文,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\r英文}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.28,0:33:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,乘客们，为了安全起见还是请你系好安全带\N{\r英文}Everyone, might be a good idea just to keep your seat belts on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.12,0:33:45.84,中文,,0,0,0,,一台发动机减速了\N{\r英文}We got one rolling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.20,0:33:50.44,中文,,0,0,0,,两台发动机都减速了\N{\r英文}We have both of them rolling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.88,0:33:56.04,中文,,0,0,0,,点火器打开\N{\r英文}Ignition start.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.36,0:34:04.69,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\r英文}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.12,0:34:07.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我现在打开辅助动力装置\N{\r英文}I'm starting the APU.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.64,0:34:13.32,中文,,0,0,0,,请再次检查安全带是否系好\N{\r英文}Just double-check your seat belts, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.48,0:34:14.48,中文,,0,0,0,,系好安全带\N{\r英文}Seat belt. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.64,0:34:15.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我能检查下你的安全带系没系好吗？\N{\r英文}Can I make sure your seatbelts are fastened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.12,0:34:17.64,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}请确认你的安全带已系好{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Make sure your seat belts are fastened.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.00,0:34:21.41,中文,,0,0,0,,请系好安全带\N{\r英文}Seat belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.24,0:34:28.08,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得出了什么事？  - 我猜是遇到鸟击了\N{\r英文}- What do you think that was?  - I think it was a bird strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.68,0:34:30.80,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那我们得返回拉瓜迪亚了  - 是的\N{\r英文}- Then we're going back to LaGuardia.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.76,0:34:32.76,中文,,0,0,0,,拿出快速检查单\N{\r英文}Get out the QRH.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.04,0:34:35.08,中文,,0,0,0,,找双发停车\N{\r英文}Loss of thrust on both engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.52,0:34:37.64,中文,,0,0,0,,SOS，这是全美航空1549\N{\r英文}Mayday, mayday, mayday. This is Cactus 1549.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.84,0:34:38.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们遭到鸟击\N{\r英文}We hit birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.00,0:34:40.84,中文,,0,0,0,,4500米保持，达美航空331\N{\r英文}Maintain 1-5000, Delta 3-3-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.00,0:34:44.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的双发都停车了，现在返回拉瓜迪亚机场\N{\r英文}We've lost thrust on both engines. We are turning back towards LaGuardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.60,0:34:46.36,中文,,0,0,0,,好的，你需要返回拉瓜迪亚？\N{\r英文}Okay, you need to return to LaGuardia?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.84,0:34:48.88,中文,,0,0,0,,- 左转航向220  - 航向220\N{\r英文}- Turn left heading 2-2-0.  - SULLY: 2-2-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.04,0:34:50.53,中文,,0,0,0,,哪台发动机停车？\N{\r英文}Which engine did you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.68,0:34:51.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}双发，双发停车{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Both. Both engines.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.00,0:34:53.00,中文,,0,0,0,,- 主管？  - 嗯？\N{\r英文}- Supe?  - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.16,0:34:54.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我这有紧急情况\N{\r英文}I have an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.88,0:34:57.88,中文,,0,0,0,,什么状况？\N{\r英文}What's the report?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.08,0:34:59.12,中文,,0,0,0,,双发停车\N{\r英文}Both engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.36,0:35:01.52,中文,,0,0,0,,- 什么？  - 双发都停车了，没有推力\N{\r英文}- What?  - Both engines gone. No thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.84,0:35:04.84,中文,,0,0,0,,知道了\N{\r英文}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.04,0:35:07.52,中文,,0,0,0,,拉瓜迪亚说可以降落在跑道13\N{\r英文}LaGuardia says go to runway 1-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.84,0:35:10.32,中文,,0,0,0,,塔台，停止起飞安排，我们有个紧急返场\N{\r英文}Tower, stop your departure. Got an emergency returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.48,0:35:12.13,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549，遭到鸟击\N{\r英文}1549, bird strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.28,0:35:14.08,中文,,0,0,0,,他的双发都停车了，要立即返航\N{\r英文}He lost both engines. Returning immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.24,0:35:15.24,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}哪台发动机？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Which engine?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.44,0:35:17.76,中文,,0,0,0,,他说2台发动机都停车了\N{\r英文}He lost thrust in both engines, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.28,0:35:21.80,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549，如果我们能给你清空跑道3，你能尝试降落在跑道13吗？\N{\r英文}Cactus 1549, if we can get it for you, do you wanna try to land runway 1 -3?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.40,0:35:25.64,中文,,0,0,0,,没法办到，我们很可能会迫降哈德逊河\N{\r英文}We are unable. We may end up in the Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.56,0:35:29.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们这有架A320要坠河\N{\r英文}I got an A320 diving for the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.92,0:35:31.60,中文,,0,0,0,,阿尔，暂停拉瓜迪亚的所有进场\N{\r英文}Al, stack all the inbounds to LaGuardia.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.76,0:35:33.41,中文,,0,0,0,,让我们先停一下\N{\r英文}Let's put a hold on the tower, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.56,0:35:34.76,中文,,0,0,0,,大伙听到了吗\N{\r英文}Come on, guys, stay on point.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.92,0:35:35.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们的右侧有什么？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}What about over to our right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.12,0:35:38.40,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}新泽西那边，泰特伯勒机场有可能吗？{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Anything in New Jersey? Maybe Teterboro?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.56,0:35:39.56,中文,,0,0,0,,泰特伯勒塔台，我需要条跑道\N{\r英文}Teterboro tower, I need a runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.72,0:35:41.37,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549需要机场紧急降落\N{\r英文}Cactus 1549 needs to go to the airport right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.52,0:35:42.88,中文,,0,0,0,,纽瓦克塔台，你们那呢？\N{\r英文}Newark tower, what have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.04,0:35:44.69,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}跑道29可以降落{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}You have runway 2-9 cleared and ready.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.84,0:35:46.25,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- 你需要紧急降落？{\i}  - 是的\N{\r英文}{\i1}- You need emergency landing?{\i}  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.40,0:35:47.40,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\r英文}Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.64,0:35:49.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你右侧有泰特伯勒机场降落\N{\r英文}Off your right side is Teterboro airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.60,0:35:54.88,中文,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\r英文}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.68,0:35:57.40,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是机长{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}This is the Captain.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.56,0:35:59.13,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}准备紧急撞击姿势{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Brace for impact.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.28,0:36:00.40,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\r英文}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.56,0:36:01.72,中文,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\r英文}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.92,0:36:03.44,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}准备，准备，准备{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Brace, brace, brace!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.80,0:36:06.28,中文,,0,0,0,,头埋下，埋好了\N{\r英文}Heads down, stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.72,0:36:08.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}准备，准备，准备{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Brace, brace, brace!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.04,0:36:11.52,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}头埋下，埋好了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Heads down, stay down!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.68,0:36:13.64,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549，右转航向280{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Cactus 1549, turn right 2-8-0.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.80,0:36:15.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你可以降落在泰特伯勒机场跑道1{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}You can land runway one Teterboro.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.64,0:36:16.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们办不到\N{\r英文}We can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.92,0:36:18.49,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们要迫降哈德逊河了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We're gonna end up in the Hudson.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.64,0:36:20.60,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉，请再说一遍，全美航空\N{\r英文}I'm sorry. Say again, Cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.56,0:36:27.96,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549，雷达信号消失\N{\r英文}Cactus 1549, radar contact lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.48,0:36:29.89,中文,,0,0,0,,KC，来这里\N{\r英文}KC, come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.08,0:36:33.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你还有纽瓦克机场，在你2点钟方向，大约11公里\N{\r英文}You also got Newark off your two o'clock in about seven miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.80,0:36:36.37,中文,,0,0,0,,千万别掉水里\N{\r英文}Don't go in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.52,0:36:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,- 长官？  - 你来接手\N{\r英文}- Sir?  - Plug in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.72,0:36:43.21,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549，如果你可以\N{\r英文}Cactus 1549, if you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.36,0:36:45.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以降落在纽瓦克机场跑道29\N{\r英文}you got runway 2-9 available at Newark.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.96,0:36:47.80,中文,,0,0,0,,在你2点钟方向，大约11公里\N{\r英文}It'll be two o'clock in seven miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.44,0:36:49.48,中文,,0,0,0,,加油啊\N{\r英文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.24,0:36:51.65,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}老天保佑{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Please, God.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.68,0:36:56.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾，帕特里克\N{\r英文}I'm sorry, Patrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.04,0:36:59.32,中文,,0,0,0,,他飞去纽瓦克了，肯定的，他只是关掉无线电来专注驾驶\N{\r英文}He's inbound to Newark, I know it. He just went off the box to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.52,0:37:00.52,中文,,0,0,0,,帕蒂\N{\r英文}Patty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.72,0:37:02.05,中文,,0,0,0,,他会跟我通话的\N{\r英文}He'll come back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.24,0:37:03.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他正飞往泰特伯勒机场\N{\r英文}He's heading to Teterboro.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.08,0:37:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要其他帮手\N{\r英文}We need other eyes and ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.56,0:37:09.08,中文,,0,0,0,,全体注意，乔治华盛顿大桥附近的各架飞机\N{\r英文}Attention, all aircraft in the vicinity of the GW.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.12,0:37:12.92,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在我们转到这一头后{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}When we come up around this bend up here,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.12,0:37:14.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们就能看见“无畏号”海洋航空航天博物馆{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}we'll see the USS Intrepid.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.04,0:37:16.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}有架空客A320正在紧急下落{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We got an A320 on emergency descent.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.12,0:37:20.72,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}全美航空1549，低空飞行在哈德逊河上方{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Cactus 1549 is low level above the Hudson.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.92,0:37:24.52,中文,,0,0,0,,这里是直升机167，麦克·坦戈号，我看到目标了\N{\r英文}This is helicopter 1-6-7, Mike Tango. I've got eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.72,0:37:26.21,中文,,0,0,0,,好，我有一架直升机在现场\N{\r英文}Okay. I got a chopper with visuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.36,0:37:28.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我要继续调度\N{\r英文}I'm staying on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:29.96,中文,,0,0,0,,他就在那里\N{\r英文}He's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.84,0:37:34.76,中文,,0,0,0,,他正飞往纽瓦克，11公里，就11公里\N{\r英文}He's headed to Newark, seven miles. It's only seven miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.72,0:37:41.04,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549，这里是离场管制，守台中，你听到了吗？\N{\r英文}Cactus 1549, this is departure control. On guard, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.80,0:37:43.48,中文,,0,0,0,,他掉下去了\N{\r英文}He's going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.36,0:37:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,全美航空1549，听得到我说话吗？\N{\r英文}Cactus 1549, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.44,0:37:50.33,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}糟了，他要掉下去了，他要撞到水面了{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Shit! He's going down! He's gonna hit the water.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.68,0:37:54.08,中文,,0,0,0,,- KC，你来接管  - 好的\N{\r英文}- KC, take his seat.  - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.76,0:38:00.92,中文,,0,0,0,,会有检测人员过来\N{\r英文}Tester's gonna come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.20,0:38:04.24,中文,,0,0,0,,做呼吸酒精检测，尿检，标准程序\N{\r英文}Breathalyzer, urine samples, it's standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.76,0:38:06.72,中文,,0,0,0,,他听上去很镇定\N{\r英文}His voice was so calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.76,0:38:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,他说哈德逊河时，我都不敢相信\N{\r英文}When he said the Hudson, I didn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.52,0:38:13.44,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是真的\N{\r英文}This isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.40,0:38:16.92,中文,,0,0,0,,水面降落肯定会机毁人亡的，亨利\N{\r英文}People don't survive water landings, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.84,0:38:25.81,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起，拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up. Pull up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.96,0:38:27.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要承受撞击了\N{\r英文}We're gonna brace.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.96,0:38:28.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起，拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up! Pull up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.24,0:38:30.28,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}30{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Thirty.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.92,0:38:32.12,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}20{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Twenty.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.88,0:38:33.88,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}10{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Ten.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.24,0:38:39.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我得挂了\N{\r英文}I'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.28,0:38:44.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我真替你遗憾，我爱你\N{\r英文}I am so sorry. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.68,0:38:47.33,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，我得挂了\N{\r英文}Yeah. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.08,0:39:00.68,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}飞机刚从纽约拉瓜迪亚机场起飞{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}It had just taken off from New York's LaGuardia Airport,{\i}
