Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.60,1:11:48.40,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}多个机场、跑道，2起成功降落{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Multiple airports, runways, two successful landings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.92,1:11:53.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只是重复下计算机的演算结果\N{\r英文}We are simply mimicking what the computer already told us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.76,1:11:57.16,中文,,0,0,0,,为了设置好今天的这套演示设备，可是折腾了不少人\N{\r英文}A lot of toes were stepped on in order to set this up for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.32,1:12:02.97,中文,,0,0,0,,坦白说，我真不明白你们两位想达到什么目的\N{\r英文}And frankly, I really don't know what you gentlemen plan to gain by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.48,1:12:05.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以现实点吗？\N{\r英文}Can we get serious now?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.40,1:12:08.44,中文,,0,0,0,,机长?\N{\r英文}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.60,1:12:10.17,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我们都听说过计算机模拟{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}We've all heard about the computer simulations{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.36,1:12:12.93,中文,,0,0,0,,现在也看了实际的模拟演示\N{\r英文}and now we are watching actual sims.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.08,1:12:15.24,中文,,0,0,0,,可让我惊讶的是\N{\r英文}But I can't quite believe
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.12,1:12:20.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你们仍然没有把人类因素考虑进去\N{\r英文}you still have not taken into account the human factor.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.72,1:12:22.05,中文,,0,0,0,,人类飞行员进行的模拟\N{\r英文}Human piloted simulations
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.20,1:12:24.04,中文,,0,0,0,,显示你可以返回机场\N{\r英文}showed that you could make it back to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.52,1:12:25.80,中文,,0,0,0,,不对，他们办不到\N{\r英文}No, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.48,1:12:29.13,中文,,0,0,0,,这些飞行员并不像人类一样行事\N{\r英文}These pilots were not behaving like human beings,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.32,1:12:31.80,中文,,0,0,0,,并不像那种初次经历的人一样应对\N{\r英文}like people who are experiencing this for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.96,1:12:33.61,中文,,0,0,0,,他们只是不像你那样应对而已\N{\r英文}Well, they may not be reacting like you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.76,1:12:35.36,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一遭遇鸟击{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Immediately after the bird strike{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.52,1:12:37.09,中文,,0,0,0,,他们就返回机场\N{\r英文}they are turning back for the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.24,1:12:39.20,中文,,0,0,0,,就像计算机演算的一样，对吧？\N{\r英文}Just as in the computer sims, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.36,1:12:40.36,中文,,0,0,0,,对\N{\r英文}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.52,1:12:43.80,中文,,0,0,0,,他们明显知道如何转向，飞哪个航向\N{\r英文}They obviously knew the turn and exactly what heading to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.00,1:12:45.33,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他们没有执行检查单{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}They did not run a check.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.48,1:12:46.84,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他没有打开辅助动力装置{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}They did not switch on the APU.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.00,1:12:49.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他们用的参数和你当时的一模一样\N{\r英文}They had all the same parameters that you faced.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.44,1:12:51.09,中文,,0,0,0,,没人警告过我们\N{\r英文}No one warned us.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.20,1:12:55.04,中文,,0,0,0,,没人想得到，你会在这种高度遭遇双发停车\N{\r英文}No one said, "You are going to lose both engines
