Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.56,1:23:40.56,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.48,1:23:42.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.44,1:23:44.44,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.92,1:23:45.92,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.08,1:23:51.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要承受撞击\N{\r英文}We're gonna brace.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.64,1:23:52.64,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.92,1:23:53.92,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}30...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Thirty...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.12,1:23:59.12,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}20...{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Twenty...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.48,1:24:00.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}拉起{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Pull up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.64,1:24:41.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我出去透个气，马上回来\N{\r英文}I need to take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.88,1:24:57.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么想的？\N{\r英文}What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.64,1:25:01.37,中文,,0,0,0,,听完驾驶舱通话录音后？\N{\r英文}Hearing the CVR just now?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.84,1:25:05.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟你说下我的想法\N{\r英文}Let me tell you what I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.72,1:25:09.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我感到无比自豪\N{\r英文}I'm just so damn proud.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.04,1:25:13.85,中文,,0,0,0,,还有你，你也在驾驶舱，没有因各种干扰而分心\N{\r英文}And you, you were right there, through all that distraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.04,1:25:15.88,中文,,0,0,0,,而局势又凶险万分\N{\r英文}With so much at stake.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.40,1:25:20.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一起扛了过来，我们缺一不可\N{\r英文}We did this together. We were a team.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.88,1:25:24.08,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢，萨利\N{\r英文}Thanks, Sully.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.48,1:25:26.60,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们恪尽职守了  - 我们恪尽职守了\N{\r英文}- We did our job.  - We did our job.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.68,1:25:47.68,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，你表现不错\N{\r英文}Hey, you did good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.24,1:25:49.24,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，各位\N{\r英文}All right, folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.40,1:25:50.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我宣布听证会继续进行\N{\r英文}I'd like to call this hearing back to order.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.92,1:25:52.60,中文,,0,0,0,,请安静下来，好吗？\N{\r英文}If we could settle, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.56,1:25:56.08,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}都请坐好{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Take your seats.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.80,1:26:04.92,中文,,0,0,0,,坦白说，这是我头一回\N{\r英文}That is honestly the first time
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.08,1:26:06.92,中文,,0,0,0,,和机长和副驾驶\N{\r英文}that I have listened to a crash recording
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.00,1:26:09.60,中文,,0,0,0,,共处一室\N{\r英文}while actually sitting
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.76,1:26:11.41,中文,,0,0,0,,听他们的坠机录音\N{\r英文}with the captain and the first officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.16,1:26:15.68,中文,,0,0,0,,真是非同寻常\N{\r英文}It's extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.20,1:26:19.72,中文,,0,0,0,,那可不是模拟\N{\r英文}That was no simulation.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.76,1:26:22.12,中文,,0,0,0,,对，不是模拟\N{\r英文}No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.76,1:26:25.00,中文,,0,0,0,,两位\N{\r英文}Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.56,1:26:29.28,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我想告知你们左翼发动机已被捞出{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I want to inform you that the left engine has been recovered.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.24,1:26:32.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们刚收到详细调查报告\N{\r英文}We just received a comprehensive report.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.28,1:26:36.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}发动机上的导流叶片{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}There was extensive damage{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.12,1:26:39.60,中文,,0,0,0,,和风扇叶片都受到了大面积损伤\N{\r英文}to both the guide vanes and fan blades of the engine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.76,1:26:42.57,中文,,0,0,0,,5个压缩机叶片断裂\N{\r英文}Five compressor blades were fractured
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.88,1:26:46.80,中文,,0,0,0,,还有8个可变导流叶片丢失\N{\r英文}and eight variable guide vanes missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.40,1:26:49.20,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是没推力?\N{\r英文}So, no thrust?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.36,1:26:50.44,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就如你证词所言{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}As you testified,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.12,1:26:53.28,中文,,0,0,0,,发动机彻底损毁\N{\r英文}it was completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.44,1:26:55.64,中文,,0,0,0,,飞机通信寻址与报告系统的数据是错误的\N{\r英文}The ACARS data was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.48,1:27:03.29,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我想分享点个人感受{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}I'd like to add something on a personal note.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.88,1:27:05.76,中文,,0,0,0,,在同其他机组成员、鸟类专家\N{\r英文}I can say with absolute confidence
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.92,1:27:08.92,中文,,0,0,0,,还有航空工程师谈过后\N{\r英文}that after speaking with the rest of the flight crew,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.68,1:27:12.28,中文,,0,0,0,,在分析过每一种场景\N{\r英文}with bird experts, aviation engineers,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.64,1:27:15.29,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}访谈了每一个责任方后\N{\r英文}after running through every scenario,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.44,1:27:17.68,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我有绝对的把握这样说{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}after interviewing each player,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.16,1:27:20.60,中文,,0,0,0,,结果的方程式仍然少了一个未知数\N{\r英文}there is still an "X" in this result
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.48,1:27:24.16,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是你，机长萨伦伯格\N{\r英文}and it's you, Captain Sullenberger.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.32,1:27:29.32,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}把你从方程中移除，计算结果就只有失败{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}Remove you from the equation, and the math just fails.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.00,1:27:32.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\r英文}I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.32,1:27:37.16,中文,,0,0,0,,不只是我，是我们所有人\N{\r英文}It wasn'tjust me. It was all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.32,1:27:40.13,中文,,0,0,0,,是杰夫和堂娜，希拉和多琳\N{\r英文}It was Jeff and Donna and Sheila and Doreen
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.96,1:27:44.52,中文,,0,0,0,,所有的乘客、救援人员\N{\r英文}and all of the passengers, the rescue workers,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.68,1:27:46.96,中文,,0,0,0,,空管人员\N{\r英文}air traffic control,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.12,1:27:49.52,中文,,0,0,0,,轮渡船员，还有警局潜水小队\N{\r英文}ferry boat crews and the scuba cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.64,1:27:53.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都尽了一份力\N{\r英文}We all did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.44,1:27:56.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们这才得以幸存\N{\r英文}We survived.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.96,1:28:04.04,中文,,0,0,0,,副驾驶斯基尔斯，你有什么想补充的吗\N{\r英文}First Officer Skiles, is there anything you'd like to add?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.52,1:28:07.64,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你不得不再经历一次\N{\r英文}Anything you would have done differently
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.84,1:28:10.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你会有什么地方做得不同吗\N{\r英文}if you had to do it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.52,1:28:12.72,中文,,0,0,0,,有\N{\r英文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.32,1:28:14.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我会选在7月份做\N{\r英文}I would have done it in July.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.72,1:28:31.05,中文,,0,0,0,,2009年1月15日
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.15,1:28:33.70,中文,,0,0,0,,有超过1200名现场急救员和7艘载有130名乘客的渡轮
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.77,1:28:36.17,中文,,0,0,0,,参与对1549航班乘客和机组成员的救援行动
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.80,1:28:40.27,中文,,0,0,0,,纽约的骄子齐心协力，整场行动仅耗时24分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.64,1:29:52.32,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}7排F座. 11排F座.{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}7F. 11F.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.48,1:29:53.48,中文,,0,0,0,,9排D座\N{\r英文}9D.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.68,1:29:54.68,中文,,0,0,0,,1排C座\N{\r英文}1C.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.84,1:29:56.80,中文,,0,0,0,,- 25排B座  - 26排B座\N{\r英文}- 25B.  - 26B.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.12,1:29:59.16,中文,,0,0,0,,- 10排B座  - 9排A座\N{\r英文}- 10B.  - 9A.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.32,1:30:02.24,中文,,0,0,0,,-13排C座  - 21排A座和B座\N{\r英文}-13C.  - 21A and B.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.80,1:30:04.48,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}155是个数字{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}155 is a number,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.08,1:30:08.56,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可当你去对应一张张面孔时{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}but when you can put faces to it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.72,1:30:13.08,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那就不只是155张了，还有其他的面孔{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}and not just 155 faces, but the other faces,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.24,1:30:17.16,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}妻子们，女儿们，儿子们，父亲们，母亲们，兄弟们{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}the wives, the daughters, the sons, the fathers, the mothers, the brothers,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.68,1:30:19.64,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}数字立马就可观起来{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}it gets to be a pretty big number pretty quickly.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.96,1:30:21.76,中文,,0,0,0,,现在是你们的机长在说话\N{\r英文}This is your captain speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.16,1:30:31.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我认为今天对我和我的组员是个特别的日子，对你们也是一样\N{\r英文}I think today was as much and as good for me and my crew as it was for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.68,1:30:35.96,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}并且因为2009年1月15日的经历{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}And because of the events of January 15, 2009,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.12,1:30:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我确信我们的心灵将会永远相通\N{\r英文}I'm convinced that we will be joined in our hearts and in our minds forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.16,1:31:39.32,中文,,0,0,0,,家里的邮件是我来保管\N{\r英文}I am the keeper of the mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.08,1:31:43.56,中文,,0,0,0,,所以全国各地的朋友写给我们的信，我都会看\N{\r英文}So I read when people from across the country write to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.72,1:31:47.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我看过你们的家人寄给我们的信\N{\r英文}And I open the letters that come to our house from your families.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.52,1:31:49.09,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}打开过贺年卡{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}And I open the Christmas cards.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.24,1:31:50.76,中文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}所以要非常感谢你们{\i}\N{\r英文}{\i1}So, thank you so much{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.92,1:31:54.08,中文,,0,0,0,,给我们家表达的祝愿\N{\r英文}for the gratitude that you've expressed to our families
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.24,1:31:56.60,中文,,0,0,0,,以及那些信件和卡片\N{\r英文}and the letters and the cards
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.76,1:32:00.40,中文,,0,0,0,,因为这一切也让我们倍感温暖\N{\r英文}because they really do make a difference to us as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.56,1:32:01.89,中文,,0,0,0,,所以要谢谢你们\N{\r英文}So, thank you.

